title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Vehicles Not Railway & Tram Accessories
description: Imports Intra Eu - Vehicles Not Railway & Tram Accessories in the United Kingdom increased to 3456.71 GBP Million in September from 2585.87 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Vehicles Not Railway & Tram Acc in the United Kingdom averaged 2617.06 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 5317.31 GBP Million in March of 2019 and a record low of 886.64 GBP Million in April of 2020. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Vehicles Not Railway & Tram.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
